          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1721060491676-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>ciabatta[s]</strong> to a baking tray and put the tray in the oven for 5 min or until hot and crusty</p><p>Carefully slice in half before serving</p><p>Add the <strong>salad </strong>to the bowl of <strong>dressing</strong> and toss until fully coated – this is your <strong>zingy</strong> <strong>salad</strong></p><p>Season the <strong>fried eggs </strong>with a grind of <strong>black pepper</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1721060495241-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1721060495241-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
