          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1721060495241-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Divide your <strong>smashed avocado </strong>between the <strong>warmed</strong> <strong>ciabatta</strong> <strong>base</strong> and <strong>lid</strong></p><p>Top the base with a handful of <strong>zingy salad</strong>, a <strong>sausage patty</strong>, a <strong>fried egg </strong>and the <strong>warmed ciabatta lid </strong>– this is your <strong>sausage, egg & avocado sandwich</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
